	Class == "Amulets" "Belts" "Body Armours" "Boots" "Bows" "Bucklers" "Crossbows" "Foci" "Gloves" "Helmets" "One Hand Maces" "Quarterstaves" "Quivers" "Rings" "Sceptres" "Shields" "Spears" "Staves" "Talismans" "Two Hand Maces" "Wands"
